    <p>
      How do they do it? There are many ways a website or browser is collecting your information. Sometimes you are
      completely aware of the information you are providing. Most of the time it is being done behind the scenes.
    </p>
    <p>
      Your IP address is a simple way to glean information about you online. Your IP address gives away information like
      your rough geographical location and your Internet Service Provider. It can identify your computer, or your local network.  I have collected your IP Address already. 
    </p>
    <p id="ipDisplay">
